  "keyFeatures": [
    "Double-entry accounting ledger with 55 chart-of-accounts entries (Debe/Haber)",
    "Two consolidation types: Generales and Hoteles (with I.S.T. 4%)",
    "Automatic ISV 15% and ISV 18% tax calculation formulas",
    "Client (empresa) management with RTN validation",
    "Excel and PDF export of consolidation records",
    "Role-based access control (admin / user) via JWT",
    "System audit log (bitácora) with categorized activity tracking",
    "Multi-layer security: rate limiting, IP behavior analysis, automatic blocking",
    "Electron desktop packaging for offline/local Windows deployment",
    "SQL Server backend with mssql connection pooling"
  ],
